WEBVTT


00:00:00.060 --> 00:00:03.960
You can decide to be rich and with God's help,

00:00:04.140 --> 00:00:08.520
it's highly doable, but you first have to think it.

00:00:09.340 --> 00:00:13.820
The difference between successful people and non successful people is

00:00:13.821 --> 00:00:14.761
here.

00:00:15.620 --> 00:00:17.800
I'm no better than none of y'all.

00:00:18.580 --> 00:00:20.540
I'm not a better person than you.

00:00:20.541 --> 00:00:22.641
I'm not a better Christian than you.

00:00:22.660 --> 00:00:26.040
God don't love me more than you, none of that.

00:00:27.620 --> 00:00:29.760
If you wanna be successful,

00:00:29.940 --> 00:00:32.360
you have to change this.

00:00:33.140 --> 00:00:35.120
This has to change.

00:00:35.940 --> 00:00:40.640
What makes it hard is your lack of belief that it can happen for you.

00:00:41.420 --> 00:00:43.100
The fact of it is, though,

00:00:43.101 --> 00:00:44.561
it's very doable.

00:00:45.060 --> 00:00:49.000
So if you're at a place in your life and you ain't happy with it,

00:00:49.140 --> 00:00:51.320
you have to change some things.

00:00:51.500 --> 00:00:56.640
But you have to make a conscious decision that you're going to change.

00:00:56.740 --> 00:00:59.520
And it's not dependent on anybody else.

00:00:59.660 --> 00:01:03.440
You have to live your life with the expectation

00:01:03.780 --> 00:01:06.520
that great things are coming your way.

00:01:07.180 --> 00:01:12.000
And that's how it works. A man is as he thinketh.

00:01:13.300 --> 00:01:16.520
God created us in his image.

00:01:17.500 --> 00:01:20.560
Now, you can't go make earth and heaven like he did,

00:01:20.820 --> 00:01:23.120
but you can make a better world for yourself.
